825
00:48:18,640 --> 00:48:23,120
'No door knobs, no letterbox.
Painted windows.

826
00:48:23,120 --> 00:48:26,280
'23 and 24 Leinster Gardens.

827
00:48:26,280 --> 00:48:28,360
'The empty houses.

828
00:48:28,360 --> 00:48:32,360
