somewhere with that.

861
00:50:14,680 --> 00:50:16,760
'I want to know how good you are.

862
00:50:16,760 --> 00:50:18,280
'Go on, show me.

863
00:50:18,280 --> 00:50:21,320
'The doctor's wife must be
