00:53:12,680 --> 00:53:14,800
Lovely when you
bring your friends round(!)

906
00:53:14,800 --> 00:53:17,960
Stop it, you.
Somebody's put a bullet in my boy.

907
00:53:17,960 --> 00:53:22,600
If I ever find out who,
